ral days, which gave Alonso enough time for a trip to Disneyland Paris, she finally left Paris for Texas, where she is a political science major at Southern Methodist University in Dallas.\", \"from\": 674, \"to\": 891, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 757, \"end\": 767, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disneyland\", \"score\": 0.9998762522224179, \"rank\": 7.854262123293393e-05, \"text\": \"Disneyland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disneyland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disneyland\"}, {\"begin\": 768, \"end\": 773, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999965296959733, \"rank\": 3.470316069796756e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 792, \"end\": 797, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999965296959733, \"rank\": 3.470316069796756e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 802, \"end\": 807, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas\", \"score\": 0.9984689007515213, \"rank\": 0.00056695197089341, \"text\": \"Texas\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas\"}, {\"begin\": 851, \"end\": 880, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southern_Methodist_University\", \"score\": 0.9883219784581767, \"rank\": 0.011172993589745639, \"text\": \"Southern Methodist University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southern_Methodist_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southern_Methodist_University\"}, {\"begin\": 884, \"end\": 890, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dallas\", \"score\": 0.9999906987457612, \"rank\": 6.915117514741058e-06, \"