rom\": 1261, \"to\": 1270}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not want to give any statement but I am not going to let lies affect me either.\\\"\", \"from\": 1272, \"to\": 1358, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any statement\", \"from\": 1295, \"to\": 1308}, {\"ngram\": \"lies\", \"from\": 1335, \"to\": 1339}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Newspapers in Paraguay had in fact carried the text of an email sent to Alonso by Paraguay's chef de mission in Paris, Larissa Schaerer, asking her to leave the Olympic village because her activities were \\\"creating an inappropriate atmosphere at the heart of Team Paraguay.\\\"\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1634, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1374, \"end\": 1382, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\", \"score\": 0.9999871824709949, \"rank\": 1.2701528081211895e-05, \"text\": \"Paraguay\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\"}, {\"begin\": 1442, \"end\": 1450, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\", \"score\": 0.9999871824709949, \"rank\": 1.2701528081211895e-05, \"text\": \"Paraguay\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\"}, {\"begin\": 1472, \"end\": 1477, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999965296959733, \"rank\": 3.470316069796756e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1479, \"end\": 1495, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larissa_Schaerer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Larissa Schaerer\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larissa_Schaerer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larissa_Schaerer\"}, {\"begin\": 1624, \"end\": 1632, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.